section_desc: Supplementary factors related to causes of morbidity classified elsewhere (Y90-Y99)
notes: ['Category Y93 is provided for use to indicate the activity of the person seeking healthcare for an injury or health condition, such as a heart attack while shoveling snow, which resulted from, or was contributed to, by the activity.  These codes are appropriate for use for both acute injuries, such as those from chapter 19, and conditions that are due to the long-term, cumulative effects of an activity, such as those from chapter 13.  They are also appropriate for use with external cause codes for cause and intent if identifying the activity provides additional information on the event.  These codes should be used in conjunction with codes for external cause status (Y99) and place of occurrence (Y92).', 'This section contains the following broad activity categories:', 'Y93.0\tActivities involving walking and running', 'Y93.1\tActivities involving water and water craft', 'Y93.2\tActivities involving ice and snow', 'Y93.3\tActivities involving climbing, rappelling, and jumping off', 'Y93.4\tActivities involving dancing and other rhythmic movement', 'Y93.5\tActivities involving other sports and athletics played individually', 'Y93.6\tActivities involving other sports and athletics played as a team or group', 'Y93.7\tActivities involving other specified sports and athletics', 'Y93.A\tActivities involving other cardiorespiratory exercise', 'Y93.B\tActivities involving other muscle strengthening exercises', 'Y93.C\tActivities involving computer technology and electronic devices', 'Y93.D\tActivities involving arts and handcrafts', 'Y93.E\tActivities involving personal hygiene and interior property and clothing maintenance', 'Y93.F\tActivities involving caregiving', 'Y93.G\tActivities involving food preparation, cooking and grilling', 'Y93.H\tActivities involving exterior property and land maintenance, building and construction', 'Y93.I\tActivities involving roller coasters and other types of external motion', 'Y93.J\tActivities involving playing musical instrument', 'Y93.K\tActivities involving animal care', 'Y93.8\tActivities, other specified', 'Y93.9\tActivity, unspecified']
